PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781963310
OL,3,CNew freight ship for Isles of Scilly
OL,4,Carrives from Vietnam
OL,6,FA new freight ship for the Isles of
OL,7,FScilly arrived in Penzance this
OL,8,Fmorning.
OL,10,FThe vessel of the Isles of Scilly
OL,11,FSteamship Group - named Menawethan -
OL,12,Farrived after a two-month journey from
OL,13,FVietnam via the Cape of Good Hope.
OL,15,FThe group will not take formal
OL,16,Fownership of Menawethan until final
OL,17,Fcontractual and legal procedures have
OL,18,Fbeen finalised in Penzance.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
