OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781963310
OL,3,CNew freight ship for Isles of Scilly
OL,4,Carrives from Vietnam
OL,6,FThe vessel will then undergo a survey
OL,7,Fby the Maritime and Coastguard Agency,
OL,8,Fwhich is a legal requirement, as well
OL,9,Fas crew training and trials at sea.
OL,11,FThe ship is built with "modern
OL,12,Fcapabilities" and "efficiency at its
OL,13,Fcore", according to the Isles of
OL,14,FScilly Steamship Group, which the
OL,15,Fcompany says will enhance freight
OL,16,Foperations between Penzance and the
OL,17,FIsles of Scilly.
OL,19,FThe vessel replaces Gry Maritha.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781963310
OL,3,CNew freight ship for Isles of Scilly
OL,4,Carrives from Vietnam
OL,6,FThe "state-of-the-art" ship features
OL,7,Fimprovements, including an enhanced
OL,8,Fcargo capacity and an improved
OL,9,Fcapacity for perishable, chilled and
OL,10,Ffrozen goods, meaning that supplies
OL,11,Fcan be transferred between the
OL,12,Fmainland and the islands more reliably
OL,13,Fall year round.
OL,15,FIt will be able to carry 12 passengers
OL,16,Fin a dedicated lounge, providing a
OL,17,Fyear-round transport link by sea.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781963310
OL,3,CNew freight ship for Isles of Scilly
OL,4,Carrives from Vietnam
OL,6,FThe vessel is designed to improve
OL,7,Freliability in all seasons, ensuring
OL,8,Fessential supplies continue to reach
OL,9,Fthe islands.
OL,11,FMenawethan was built at Piriou's
OL,12,Fshipyard in Ho Chi Minh alongside
OL,13,FScillonian IV - the Isles of Scilly
OL,14,FSteamship Group's new passenger
OL,15,Fvessel, which is expected to enter
OL,16,Fservice in 2027.
OL,18,FThe two new ships represent a #40
OL,19,Fmillion investment in the future of
OL,20,Fthe islands' lifeline transport links.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781963310
OL,3,CNew freight ship for Isles of Scilly
OL,4,Carrives from Vietnam
OL,6,FStuart Reid, Chief Executive of the
OL,7,FIsles of Scilly Steamship Group, said:
OL,8,F"Menawethan's arrival into Penzance is
OL,9,Fa hugely proud moment for the
OL,10,FSteamship Group. After years of
OL,11,Fplanning, design and construction, it
OL,12,Fis fantastic to see her finally arrive
OL,13,Fin Cornwall.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
