OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781963310
OL,3,CNew freight ship for Isles of Scilly
OL,4,Carrives from Vietnam
OL,6,F"This vessel is a major investment in
OL,7,Fthe future of the Isles of Scilly. She
OL,8,Fwill provide greater freight capacity,
OL,9,Fimproved resilience and enhanced
OL,10,Ffacilities for our customers. We will
OL,11,Fnow begin the final phase of crew
OL,12,Ftraining and familiarisation before
OL,13,Fbringing Menawethan into service."
OL,15,FThere will be an official naming
OL,16,Fceremony on the 8th July in the Isles
OL,17,Fof Scilly.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
